high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.compilers

Class AbstractStructTupleCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.compilers.AbstractRecordCompiler
      • high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.compilers.AbstractStructTupleCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompiler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StructCompiler, TupleCompiler

    public class AbstractStructTupleCompiler
extends AbstractRecordCompiler
    This class generalizes the compilation of struct-definitions and tuple-definitions.

    Note: Design-definitions are technically records, but they are compiled very differently.
